videos.description: Richard Newton runs one yard for a touchdown to put Washington on the board first.

videos.description: Cameron Williams intercepts Matt Fink's pass attempt, then Salvon Ahmed fumbles at the goal line but it is recovered by Andre Baccellia to put Washington up 14-0 over USC.
